<Layout title='Plasterers & Painters in Harefield | Hancock' description='Plastering and painting in Harefield. Fixed-price quotes from City & Guilds certified contractors covering Harefield and the surrounding area.' activePage='areas'>
<section style="position:relative;height:380px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;">
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(15).webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center 35%;"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(15,23,42,0.9) 0%,rgba(15,23,42,0.45) 60%,rgba(15,23,42,0.15) 100%);"></div>
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px 52px;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;">
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin:0 0 12px;"><a href="/" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Home</a> / <a href="/areas" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Areas</a> / Harefield</p>
    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:12px;">
      <h1 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(34px,5vw,58px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.05;">Harefield</h1>
      <span style="background:#0C7BA8;color:#ffffff;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:4px;letter-spacing:0.06em;white-space:nowrap;">HOME BASE</span>
    </div>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:17px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);margin:0;">UB9 · Our base of operations. All 14 services available locally.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:64px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;gap:64px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
    <div style="flex:2;min-width:280px;">
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">Our home area</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,32px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 20px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Hancock Plastering &amp; Painting is based at 3 Anderson Close, Harefield UB9 6HF.</h2>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 16px;">Harefield is a village in the London Borough of Hillingdon — historically a working village that retains its character despite the urban expansion around it. The housing stock is a mix of Victorian and Edwardian cottages in the village centre, interwar semis on the approach roads, and some modern development.</p>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">Being based here means we're genuinely local — we know the housing stock, we know what problems come up regularly, and our travel time is minimal. If you're in Harefield or the UB9 postcode area, you're getting the team at their doorstep.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:220px;">
      <div style="background:#E0FAFF;border:1px solid #0C7BA8;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;">
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin:0 0 16px;">Based here</p>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;">
          <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(17,173,226,0.2);padding-bottom:10px;"><span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#0F172A;">Address</span><span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;">UB9 6HF</span></div>
          <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(17,173,226,0.2);padding-bottom:10px;"><span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#0F172A;">Phone</span><a href="tel:07734903439" style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;text-decoration:none;">07734 903439</a></div>
          <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;"><span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#0F172A;">Services</span><span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;">All 14</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:64px 24px;background:#F8FAFC;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;gap:64px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:300px;">
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">The village we know best</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,30px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 20px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">From the High Street cottages to the hospital estates.</h2>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 16px;">Harefield sits at the very north-west corner of Greater London, surrounded by Green Belt countryside, the Colne Valley lakes, and the Hertfordshire and Buckinghamshire borders. The <strong>village centre and High Street</strong> hold Victorian and Edwardian cottages — solid-brick, often with lime plaster behind later finishes — while the roads toward <strong>Harefield Hospital</strong> and the village edges bring interwar semis and pockets of postwar and modern housing.</p>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 16px;">Because we live and work here, we know these streets intimately — which terraces sit on the clay, which cottages have the original lath-and-plaster ceilings, and which estates were built with the rendered and pebble-dashed elevations that need maintaining. There's no learning curve on a Harefield job.</p>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">It also means we can be there fast — for a quote, for a small repair, or to take a look at a problem before it gets worse. Being your local plasterer isn't a marketing line here; it's literally true.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:300px;">
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">What neighbours ask for</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,30px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 20px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Everything — it's home.</h2>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 16px;">All fourteen services run locally, from a single skimmed ceiling to a full exterior render and repaint. The village cottages bring period repair, lime-compatible plastering, and sash window work; the suburban semis bring extension plastering, crack repairs, and refit re-skims; the rendered estates bring exterior maintenance and masonry painting.</p>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 16px;">A good share of our Harefield work comes by word of mouth — one neighbour recommending another. That's the way we like it, and it's why the standard never drops on a local job.</p>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">Fixed price agreed up front, the same qualified pair on the tools throughout, and a tidy site at the end of every day.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 24px;">Working in Harefield</p>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:20px;">
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">On the doorstep</h3>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">We're based at 3 Anderson Close, UB9 6HF. There's no travel time and no callout cost on a Harefield job — we can often look the same week you call.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Every service, locally</h3>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">All fourteen services are available in Harefield — plastering, rendering, Venetian, sash windows, decorating, the lot. Nothing is subcontracted out.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Period &amp; modern</h3>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">We handle the lime plaster on a High Street cottage and the gypsum skim on a new extension with equal care — the right method for the wall in front of us.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Clean, tidy, insured</h3>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Dust sheets down, surfaces protected, site swept daily. Fully insured and City &amp; Guilds qualified — and your actual neighbours.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:0;">
  <div style="position:relative;height:clamp(300px,42vw,440px);">
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(2).webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center;"></div>
